Ana,

This sounds like the same setup for which fisheries scientists often use an "Age-Length Key."  Here is one resource with a short description of the problem and one algorithmic solution from the fisheries literature -- http://fishr.wordpress.com/vignettes/ (sixth bulleted link on that page ... some of the code in that document is out-of-date, if you use that method let me know and I can explain how to update it).

By the way, I am not familiar with grofit but I would suspect that it fits models with age as the independent variable, not the dependent variable that your question implies.

Good luck with your work.

